### Hadith 1:100

*Narrated 'Abdullah bin 'Amr bin Al' As:*

I heard Allah's Apostle saying, "Allah does not take away the knowledge,
by taking it away from (the hearts of) the people, but takes it away by
the death of the religious learned men till when none of the (religious
learned men) remains, people will take as their leaders ignorant persons
who when consulted will give their verdict without knowledge. So they
will go astray and will lead the people astray."

